OL,7,
OL,8,GThe BBC's director of nations says he
OL,9,Gdoesn't think the BBC is trying to take
OL,10,Gthe 'Local' out of Local Radio as
OL,11,Gproposed changes to the network of
OL,12,Gstations in England continue to face
OL,13,Gstrong criticism.
OL,15,
OL,16,FSpeaking to BBC Radio Derby's Ian Skye,
OL,17,FRhodri Talfan Davies admitted he had
OL,18,Freceived "hundreds and hundreds of
OL,19,Fletters" since the proposals were first
OL,20,Fannounced. He was criticised on-air for
OL,21,Ffailing to consult audiences and staff.
