OL,7,
OL,8,FThe BBC plans to cut back local radio
OL,9,Fprogrammes to run between 6am and 2pm
OL,10,Fon weekdays. During the remaining
OL,11,Fhours, local stations would carry a
OL,12,Frange of national, regional and
OL,13,Fsub-regional programmes, except when
OL,14,Flocal stations broadcast live sport.
OL,16,
OL,17,FThe BBC says the changes are needed in
OL,18,Forder to reallocate resources to online
OL,19,Fservices and local podcasts.
