OL,7,
OL,8,FDavies admitted he'd received letters
OL,9,Fexpressing concern over plans for
OL,10,Fweekends and sharing programmes across
OL,11,Fcounty boundaries.
OL,13,
OL,14,FHe told Ian Skye the BBC was listening
OL,15,Fto concerns from MPs, stakeholders,
OL,16,Flocal authorities and audiences,
OL,17,Femphasising the plans were still just
OL,18,Fproposals.
