OL,7,
OL,8,FAn urgent question was raised in the
OL,9,FHouse of Commons last week when culture
OL,10,Fminister Julia Lopez confirmed the DCMS
OL,11,Fhadn't been briefed on the plans prior
OL,12,Fto publication. The minister confirmed
OL,13,Fshe would be meeting BBC bosses.
OL,15,
OL,16,FMeanwhile, proposals to merge the BBC
OL,17,FNews Channel with its international
OL,18,Fcounterpart continue with less
OL,19,Fbacklash.
