OL,7,
OL,8,FThe channel launched 25 years ago today
OL,9,Fas BBC News 24. Unlike 5 years ago, the
OL,10,Foccasion was not marked by the BBC on a
OL,11,Fday dominated by rolling news coverage
OL,12,Fof the US midterms simulcast with BBC
OL,13,FWorld News.
OL,15,
OL,16,FAhead of April's changes, UK-specific
OL,17,Foutput on the channel continues to
OL,18,Fdwindle. Last month saw the long
OL,19,Frunning Film Review segment come to an
OL,20,Fend.
